### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Create a student
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Student",
  "usn": "CSE2021999",
  "email": "test.student@example.edu",
  "department": "Computer Science",
  "semester": 6,
  "marks": 84,
  "subjects": [
    { "code": "CS601", "name": "Distributed Systems", "marks": 88 },
    { "code": "CS602", "name": "Data Mining", "marks": 80 }
  ]
}

###

### Get students filtered by mark range and sorted descending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students?minMarks=80&maxMarks=95&sort=desc

###

### Update an existing student (replace :id with actual value)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/students/{{studentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marks": 89,
  "semester": 7
}

###

### Delete a student
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/students/{{studentId}}

###

### Aggregation: Average marks grouped by semester
GET http://localhost:3000/api/analytics/average-by-semester?minMarks=70

###

### Aggregation: Top performers by department
GET http://localhost:3000/api/analytics/top-performers?limit=3

